data.description: Welcome home, this 4 bedroom 2 bath home is move in ready and less than 2 years old. Tile in entry, kitchen, and all wet areas, spacious kitchen with large island and stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinet space with a pantry. Open concept with split bedrroms. Ceiling fans in bedrooms and living room, Primary bath has large stand up shower and an oversized walk in closet. Spacious backyard with a covered patio for entertaining. Located near shopping and minutes from Chisholm Trail Tollway.
